remarks.format: ## Remarks If the set operation is the copy-back of a late-bound expression being passed as a `ByRef` parameter, `OptimisticSet` is used to determine whether the set operation will work, as the latebound expression may result in a read-only property or a method. For more information see the CopyBack parameter of <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.CompilerServices.NewLateBinding.LateCall%2A>.
